About

Ngành Nghĩa Sĩ (the Companion Division)’s motto is “Chinh Phục!”, meaning “conquer”. This division wears yellow scarves, representing the rising sun on the horizon and the brightness of an age preparing to step into the world. This division consists of members from ages 13 to 15 years old who comprise three levels: Levels 1, 2, and 3
